le=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/slot\"><code>&lt;slot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/source\"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/spacer\"><code>&lt;spacer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard obsolete\" id=\"sect3\"><p><strong>Veraltet:</strong> Dieses Feature ist veraltet. Obwohl es in manchen Browsern immer noch funktioniert, wird von seiner Benutzung abgeraten, da es jederzeit entfernt werden kann. Es sollte daher nicht mehr verwendet werden.</p></div></div>\n\n<p>Das HTML Element &lt;marquee&gt; wird dazu benutzt um ein scrollendes Textfeld einzufügen. Sie können mithilfe der Attribute kontrollieren, was passiert, wenn der Text das Ende des Textfeldes erreicht.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect4\">\n<p>Das&nbsp;<code>&lt;marquee&gt;</code>&nbsp;Element ist&nbsp;<strong>veraltet</strong>&nbsp;und muss bzw. soll nicht mehr verwendet werden.&nbsp;Obwohl manche Browser es immernoch unterstützen, ist es nicht erforderlich. Es wird davon abgeraten, dieses Tag zu benutzen, da es das schlimmste ist, was Sie ihren Besuchern antun können.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"behavior\"><a id=\"attr-behavior\" href=\"#attr-behavior\"><b><code>behavior</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Bestimmt, wie sich der Text innerhalb des marquee-tags bewegt. Mögliche Optionen send \"scroll\", \"slide\" und \"alternate\". Der Standardwert&nbsp;ist \"scroll\" und wird automatisch benutzt, falls kein Wert definiert wird.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bgcolor\"><a id=\"attr-bgcolor\" href=\"#attr-bgcolor\"><b><code>bgcolor</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Bestimmt die Hintergrundfarbe mittels einer&nbsp;der Standardfarben, dem RGB- bzw. dem Hexadezimalwert.</dd>\n <dt id=\"direction\"><a id=\"attr-direction\" href=\"#attr-direction\"><b><code>direction</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Legt die Bewegungsrichtung innerhalb des marquee-tags fest. Mögliche Optionen sind \"left\", \"right\", \"up\" und \"down\". Der Standardwert ist \"left\" und wird automatisch benutzt, falls kein Wert definiert wird.</dd>\n <dt id=\"height\"><a id=\"attr-height\" href=\"#attr-height\"><b><code>height</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Definiert die Höhe in Pixel- oder Prozentwerten.</dd>\n <dt id=\"hspace\"><a id=\"attr-hspace\" href=\"#attr-hspace\"><b><code>hspace</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Definiert den horizontalen Außenabstand.</dd>\n <dt id=\"loop\"><a id=\"attr-loop\" href=\"#attr-loop\"><b><code>loop</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Definiert, wie oft die Aktion (scroll, slide, alternate) ausgeführt wird. Der Standardwert ist -1, was bedeutet, dass der Inhalt des Marquee-tags in Dauerschleife dargestellt wird.</dd>\n <dt id=\"scrollamount\"><a id=\"attr-scrollamount\" href=\"#attr-scrollamount\"><b><code>scrollamount</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Definiert&nbsp;den Wert eines Intervalls in Pixel. Der Standardwert beträgt 6.</dd>\n <dt id=\"scrolldelay\"><a id=\"attr-scrolldelay\" href=\"#attr-scrolldelay\"><b><code>scrolldelay</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Definiert den Intervall zwischen jeder Bewegung in Millisekunden. Der Standardwert ist 85. <strong>Merke:</strong> &nbsp;Jeder Wert, der kleiner als 60 ist, wird ignoriert und der Wert 60 wird stattdessen verwendet, außer \"truespeed\" ist definiert.</dd>\n <dt id=\"truespeed\"><a id=\"attr-truespeed\" href=\"#attr-truespeed\"><b><code>truespeed</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Standardmäßig werden scrolldelays, die kleiner als 60 sind ignoriert. Wenn \"truespeed\" verwendet wird, ist dies jedoch nicht der Fall.</dd>\n <dt id=\"vspace\"><a id=\"attr-vspace\" href=\"#attr-vspace\"><b><code>vspace</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Definiert den vertikalen Außenabstand in Pixel- oder Prozentwerten.</dd>\n <dt id=\"width\"><a id=\"attr-width\" href=\"#attr-width\"><b><code>width</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Definiert die Breite in Pixel- oder Prozentwerten.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"event_handlers","title":"Event-Handler","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"onbounce\"><a id=\"attr-onbounce\" href=\"#attr-onbounce\"><b><code>onbounce</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Startet, wenn der Text das Ende des zuvor definierten Marquee-tags erreicht hat. Diese Option ist jedoch nur verfügbar, wenn das Attribut \"alternate\" als \"behavior\" verwendet wird.</dd>\n <dt id=\"onfinish\"><a id=\"attr-onfinish\" href=\"#attr-onfinish\"><b><code>onfinish</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Startet, wenn das Attribut \"loop\" abgeschlossen ist. Diese Option ist jedoch nur verfügbar, wenn für das Attribut \"loop\" ein größerer Wert als 0 gewählt wurde.</dd>\n <dt id=\"onstart\"><a id=\"attr-onstart\" href=\"#attr-onstart\"><b><code>onstart</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>Startet gleichzeitig mit dem Marquee-tag.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methoden","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"start\">start</dt>\n <dd>Startet das Marquee-tag.</dd>\n <dt id=\"stop\">stop</dt>\n <dd>Stoppt das Marquee-tag.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Dieser Text bewegt sich von rechts nach links<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">direction</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>up<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Dieser Text bewegt sich von unten nach oben<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">direction</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>down<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>250<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>200<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">behavior</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>alternate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>solid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">behavior</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>alternate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Dieser Text prallt am Rand ab.\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Beispiele\" id=\"frame_examples\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Erklärung</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/obsolete.html#the-marquee-element-2\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;marquee&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>Wird veraltet zugunsten von CSS dargestellt, jedoch muss die erwartete \"behavior\"&nbsp;für die umgekehrte Kompatibilität festgelegt werden.</p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/obsolete.html#the-marquee-element-0\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;marquee&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Wird veraltet zugunsten von CSS dargestellt, jedoch muss die erwartete \"behavior\" für die umgekehrte Kompatibilität festgelegt werden.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_kompatibiltät","title":"Browser Kompatibiltät","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect5\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect6\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7 oder früher)</td>\n   <td>2.0</td>\n   <td>7.2</td>\n   <td>1.2</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>truespeed</code> attribute</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2008-06-17.\">3.0</a> (1.9)</td>\n   <td>4.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>hspace/vspace</code> attribute</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2008-06-17.\">3.0</a> (1.9)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>loop</code> attribute</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2008-06-17.\">3.0</a> (1.9)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>truespeed</code> attribute</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>hspace/vspace</code> attribute</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>loop</code> attribute</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Attribute","id":"attribute"},{"text":"Event-Handler","id":"event_handlers"},{"text":"Methoden","id":"methods"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibiltät","id":"browser_kompatibiltät"}],"summary":"Das HTML Element <marquee> wird dazu benutzt um ein scrollendes Textfeld einzufügen. Sie können mithilfe der Attribute kontrollieren, was passiert, wenn der Text das Ende des Textfeldes erreicht.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<marquee>: The Marquee element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<marquee> : l'élément de fronton (obsolète)","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<marquee>: マーキー要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"marquee","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"<marquee>：捲動元素（已過時）","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/html/element/marquee","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/html/element/marquee/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee","title":"<marquee>"}],"pageTitle":"<marquee> - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}